- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper proposes an adaptive routing approach to improve network efficiency and performance. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly mention security or cryptography, but it may be relevant in the context of inter-datacenter network security. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a less likely category as the paper does not focus on information theory concepts, but it may be relevant in the context of flow size distributions and network capacity.
